column5: CYCC Ive seen this happen so many times now Uninformed traders getting trapped by a sellside pump Heres how it works guysThree or 4 hedge funds buy the majority of the float no tutes here They then work together to drive the price up or down according to their preference They have the power to put a tamper on any rally to keep the price low for accumulation This happens after selling into a massive rally like the one we just had on the Roth recommendation They made sure it didnt go too far above the dollar mark to keep previous underwater retail longs trapped and the misery index high Simultaneously they added to that misery index by trapping a whole new batch of traders under a dollar This new batch will grow restless and leave Theyll buy those shares and do it again with another piece of analyst hype Its the perfect company to execute this strategy on Unproven and proven cooperativeOnly news will move this and Junes IRB wont move the needle enough StillShow More
